    options = RestClientOptions(access_token=token)

    async with NodestyApiClient(options) as client:
        dedicated_id = "your-dedicated-id"
        res = await client.dedicated_server.get_hardware_components(dedicated_id)

        if res.success and res.data:
            print("DonanÄ±m BileÅŸenleri:")
            for part in res.data:
                print(f"- {part.component}: {part.model} {part.value}{part.value_suffix}")
        else:
            print(f"DonanÄ±m bileÅŸenleri getirilirken hata oluÅŸtu: {res.error}")


if __name__ == "__main__":
    asyncio.run(get_dedicated_info())
```

### ğŸ›¡ï¸ GÃ¼venlik DuvarÄ±

```python
import asyncio
import os
from nodesty_api_client import NodestyApiClient, RestClientOptions
from nodesty_api_client.models.firewall import FirewallCreateRuleData


async def manage_firewall():
    token = os.environ.get("NODESTY_API_TOKEN")
    options = RestClientOptions(access_token=token)

    async with NodestyApiClient(options) as client:
        service_id = "your-service-id"
        ip_address = "your-ip-address"

        # Yeni bir kural oluÅŸtur
        rule_data = FirewallCreateRuleData(port=25565, app_id=123)
        create_res = await client.firewall.create_rule(service_id, ip_address, rule_data)

        if create_res.success:
            print("GÃ¼venlik duvarÄ± kuralÄ± baÅŸarÄ±yla oluÅŸturuldu.")
        else:
            print(f"Kural oluÅŸturulurken hata oluÅŸtu: {create_res.error}")

        # SaldÄ±rÄ± kayÄ±tlarÄ±nÄ± getir
        logs_res = await client.firewall.get_attack_logs(service_id, ip_address)
        if logs_res.success and logs_res.data:
            print("SaldÄ±rÄ± KayÄ±tlarÄ±:")
            for log in logs_res.data:
                print(f"- BaÅŸlangÄ±Ã§: {log.started_at}, VektÃ¶rler: {log.vectors}")
        else:
            print(f"SaldÄ±rÄ± kayÄ±tlarÄ± getirilirken hata oluÅŸtu: {logs_res.error}")


if __name__ == "__main__":
    asyncio.run(manage_firewall())
```

## ğŸ—ï¸ API YanÄ±t YapÄ±sÄ±

TÃ¼m API Ã§aÄŸrÄ±larÄ± `ApiResponse<T>` dÃ¶ner:

```python
from typing import TypeVar, Generic, Optional
from pydantic import BaseModel

T = TypeVar('T')


class ApiResponse(BaseModel, Generic[T]):
    success: bool
    error: Optional[str] = None
    data: Optional[T] = None
```

## âš™ï¸ YapÄ±landÄ±rma SeÃ§enekleri

```python
from nodesty_api_client import RestClientOptions
from datetime import timedelta

options = RestClientOptions(access_token="YOUR_API_TOKEN")
    .with_timeout(timedelta(seconds=30))
    .with_retry(3)
    .with_rate_limit_offset(timedelta(milliseconds=50))
```

## ğŸ“š API Servisleri

### ğŸ‘¤ User Service (`client.user`)

| Metod                   | AÃ§Ä±klama                   | Endpoint                       |
|-------------------------|----------------------------|--------------------------------|
| `get_current_user()`    | KullanÄ±cÄ± profilini al     | `GET /users/@me`               |
| `get_services()`        | Hizmetleri listele         | `GET /services`                |
| `get_tickets()`         | Destek biletlerini listele | `GET /tickets`                 |
| `get_ticket_by_id(id)`  | Belirli bileti getir       | `GET /tickets/{id}`            |
| `get_invoices()`        | FaturalarÄ± listele         | `GET /users/@me/invoices`      |
| `get_invoice_by_id(id)` | Belirli faturayÄ± getir     | `GET /users/@me/invoices/{id}` |
| `get_sessions()`        | Aktif oturumlarÄ± getir     | `GET /users/@me/sessions`      |

### ğŸ–¥ï¸ VPS Service (`client.vps`)

| Metod                        | AÃ§Ä±klama                | Endpoint                                  |
|------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| `perform_action(id, action)` | VPS eylemi gerÃ§ekleÅŸtir | `POST /services/{id}/vps/action`          |
| `get_backups(id)`            | Yedekleri getir         | `GET /services/{id}/vps/backups`          |
| `restore_backup(id, data)`   | Geri yÃ¼kleme yap        | `POST /services/{id}/vps/backup/restore`  |
| `change_password(id, data)`  | Åifre deÄŸiÅŸtir          | `POST /services/{id}/vps/change-password` |
| `get_graphs(id)`             | Ä°statistikleri al       | `GET /services/{id}/vps/graphs`           |
| `get_details(id)`            | VPS detaylarÄ±           | `GET /services/{id}/vps/info`             |
| `get_os_templates(id)`       | OS ÅŸablonlarÄ±nÄ± getir   | `GET /services/{id}/vps/os-templates`     |
| `reinstall(id, data)`        | Yeniden kurulum         | `POST /services/{id}/vps/reinstall`       |
| `get_tasks(id)`              | GÃ¶revleri getir         | `GET /services/{id}/vps/tasks`            |

### ğŸ”§ Dedicated Service (`client.dedicated_server`)

| Metod                         | AÃ§Ä±klama          | Endpoint                                        |
|-------------------------------|-------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| `perform_action(id, action)`  | Eylem Ã§alÄ±ÅŸtÄ±r    | `POST /services/{id}/dedicated/action`          |
| `get_hardware_components(id)` | DonanÄ±m detaylarÄ± | `GET /services/{id}/dedicated/hardware`         |
| `get_details(id)`             | Sunucu bilgisi    | `GET /services/{id}/dedicated/info`             |
| `get_os_templates(id)`        | OS ÅŸablonlarÄ±     | `GET /services/{id}/dedicated/os-templates`     |
| `get_reinstall_status(id)`    | Kurulum durumu    | `GET /services/{id}/dedicated/reinstall-status` |
| `reinstall(id, data)`         | Yeniden kur       | `POST /services/{id}/dedicated/reinstall`       |
| `get_tasks(id)`               | GÃ¶revleri getir   | `GET /services/{id}/dedicated/tasks`            |

### ğŸ›¡ï¸ Firewall Service (`client.firewall`)

| Metod                                               | AÃ§Ä±klama                     | Endpoint                                               |
|-----------------------------------------------------|------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------|
| `get_attack_logs(id, ip)`                           | SaldÄ±rÄ± kayÄ±tlarÄ±nÄ± getir    | `GET /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/attack-logs`         |
| `get_attack_notification_settings(id, ip)`          | Bildirim ayarlarÄ±            | `GET /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/attack-notification` |
| `update_attack_notification_settings(id, ip, data)` | Bildirim ayarlarÄ±nÄ± gÃ¼ncelle | `PUT /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/attack-notification` |
| `delete_reverse_dns(id, ip)`                        | rDNS kaldÄ±r                  | `DELETE /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rdns`             |
| `get_reverse_dns(id, ip)`                           | rDNS bilgisi                 | `GET /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rdns`                |
| `upsert_reverse_dns(id, ip, rdns_data)`             | rDNS ayarla                  | `PUT /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rdns`                |
| `delete_rule(id, ip, rule_id)`                      | Kural sil                    | `DELETE /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rules/{rule_id}`  |
| `get_rules(id, ip)`                                 | KurallarÄ± getir              | `GET /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rules`               |
| `create_rule(id, ip, data)`                         | Kural oluÅŸtur                | `POST /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/rules`              |
| `get_statistics(id, ip)`                            | Ä°statistikleri getir         | `GET /services/{id}/firewall/{ip}/stats`               |

## ğŸ” GÃ¼venlik Ä°puÃ§larÄ±

- API token'Ä±nÄ±zÄ± doÄŸrudan kodda tutmayÄ±n. Ortam deÄŸiÅŸkenlerinden (env vars) veya gÃ¼venli bir yapÄ±landÄ±rma dosyasÄ±ndan
  alÄ±n
- Her `ApiResponse` sonrasÄ± `.success` Ã¶zelliÄŸini kontrol edin
- HatalarÄ± uygun try-except bloklarÄ± veya if-else yapÄ±larÄ±yla detaylÄ± olarak yÃ¶netin

## ğŸš€ Performans Ã–nerileri

- Asenkron iÅŸlemleri `asyncio.gather()` ile paralel Ã§alÄ±ÅŸtÄ±rÄ±n
- Gecikmeleri azaltmak iÃ§in `RestClientOptions` iÃ§inde timeout ve rate limit ayarlarÄ±nÄ± yapÄ±landÄ±rÄ±n
- Uygulama baÅŸÄ±nda `NodestyApiClient`'i bir kere oluÅŸturun ve tÃ¼m uygulamanÄ±z boyunca tekrar kullanÄ±n (`async with`
  ifadesi ile otomatik kapanmasÄ±nÄ± saÄŸlayabilirsiniz)

## ğŸ§ª Test Ã–rneÄŸi

